### ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### Device API — HTTP Test File
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@apiUrl  = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1
@deviceId = ba5a5ae1-6d08-4830-b7c6-dd6899dc0414

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### Root & Health
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Hello World
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### Devices — CRUD
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create Device (available — default state)
POST {{apiUrl}}/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
  "brand": "Apple"
}

###

### Create Device (explicit state)
POST {{apiUrl}}/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Galaxy S24 Ultra V2",
  "brand": "Samsung V2",
  "state": "inactive"
}

###

### Create Device (in-use state)
POST {{apiUrl}}/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pixel 9",
  "brand": "Google",
  "state": "in-use"
}

###

### Create Device (inactive state)
POST {{apiUrl}}/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "OnePlus 12",
  "brand": "OnePlus",
  "state": "inactive"
}

###

### Get Device by ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/devices/{{deviceId}}

###

### List All Devices
GET {{apiUrl}}/devices

###

### List Devices — filter by brand
GET {{apiUrl}}/devices?brand=Apple

###

### List Devices — filter by state
GET {{apiUrl}}/devices?state=in-use

###

### List Devices — filter by brand and state
GET {{apiUrl}}/devices?brand=Samsung&state=available

###

### Patch Device — update name only
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/devices/{{deviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max"
}

###

### Patch Device — update brand only
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/devices/{{deviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "Apple Inc."
}

###

### Patch Device — update state only
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/devices/{{deviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": "in-use"
}

###

### Patch Device — update multiple fields
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/devices/{{deviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Galaxy S24",
  "brand": "Samsung",
  "state": "inactive"
}

###

### Delete Device
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/devices/{{deviceId}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### Error Cases
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create Device — missing required fields (expects 400)
POST {{apiUrl}}/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Incomplete Device"
}

###

### Create Device — invalid state (expects 400)
POST {{apiUrl}}/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bad State Device",
  "brand": "Test",
  "state": "broken"
}

###

### Get Device — not found (expects 404)
GET {{apiUrl}}/devices/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###

### Get Device — invalid ID format (expects 400)
GET {{apiUrl}}/devices/not-a-uuid

###

### Delete Device — not found (expects 404)
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/devices/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###

### Patch Device — invalid state (expects 400)
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/devices/{{deviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": "destroyed"
}

###

### Patch Device — empty name (expects 400)
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/devices/{{deviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}
